name: Fang
body:
### Welcome to FANG
FANG is an open source Python based development language that is meant to be easy. Mostly meant for people who want to start coding but don't want to start a huge development language that has 1000 paged book on it. Cough Cough [*Python*](https://www.chapters.indigo.ca/en-ca/books/product/9781449355739-item.html?mkwid=sKLCrs73h_dc&pcrid=44154474422&pkw=&pmt=&s_campaign=goo-Shopping_Books&gclid=CjwKEAiAuKy1BRCY5bTuvPeopXcSJAAq4OVsq0SJm_mEwQuYQCxgmzKZ7F3f4BvZjt_Q4cbj7ZsmVRoC6Pjw_wcB) Cough Cough

### Get started
Well first you will need to download it! [Click here](https://github.com/Merryfurr/FANG/releases) to download a FANG stable release, then head over to the [FANG Offical Wiki](https://github.com/Merryfurr/FANG/wiki) to see how to make your first program called "Hello World" and then export it!

### Authors and Contributors
+ Merryfurr [(Profile)](https://github.com/Merryfurr)

### Support
To get help with FANG issues go to the [issues](https://github.com/Merryfurr/FANG/issues) page on the GitHub repo.
